{
  "stem": "27543.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was the biggest.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had over four trucks going every two weeks up to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The bottom was the bacon, the lard, the butter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "On the top was eggs, chicken, cheese, turkey.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I had a thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They paid everything in dollar.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I had the right to have dollars on me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I never had a-- you know how it is.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's-- that what was to be my last trip.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was not legal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You asked me--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was black market.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You ask me a question.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'll tell you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everybody done it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody done it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, there was organized-- there was every-- don't forget in Vienna, at that time, you couldn't get nothing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in there, in all of those countries, in Vienna, at that time, was over 100 Hungarian Christians who was with coal and diamonds and everything.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They the one who made the whole business.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "End of it, I didn't want to do it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE]-- [INAUDIBLE] says, [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "George, ?] you got enough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You got enough.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But you know, the money, it was coming in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If we wanted to buy a bag of sugar, you needed a bag-- there-- there, you know, there was no money. 100 blue money, 50 gray money, this in color money.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Even-- you didn't even know what you payed for something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The money was coming in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You wouldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "People got millionaire.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That's the reason you see so many big Hungarian guys is all full of money.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They're multimillionaire.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They didn't have time to stop the black market.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was cut.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "At that time, the captain was named Dr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He says to me, [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "George, ?] get out of this business.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I had, at that time, 100 Napoleon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That's a gold 20 franc.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It's a rooster on it.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
